These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, zombie, satire
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter
1. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the architect is the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | disaster | zombie |
| Job    | engineer    | firefighter | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
House: townhouse, art-deco, futuristic
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
3. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the art-deco house is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| House   | futuristic    | art-deco     | townhouse        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
House: gothic-revival, colonial, cottage
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the colonial house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| House         | cottage     | colonial | gothic-revival |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, balloon-flower, aconite
1. the person watching sports movies is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Flower         | tulip  | balloon-flower | aconite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, d&b, electronic
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the fan of folk##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | electronic     | folk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, collecting, filmmaking
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, tiparillo, swisher
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the swisher-smoker is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | collecting | filmmaking | baking   |
| Cigar   | swisher     | prince    | tiparillo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, chef, scientist
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the chef is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the journalist is between the owner of the turtle and the scientist##2
3. the journalist is on the left of the chef##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Job   | scientist | journalist | chef |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, cain, bolivar
1. the siglo-smoker is between the cain-smoker and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the bolivar-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Cigar    | cain    | siglo | bolivar     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk   | tea  | hot-chocolate  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
3 different games are played: billiard, chess, snooker
There 3 different types of food: corn, garlic, pineapple
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Game   | billiard    | snooker      | chess |
| Food       | garlic | pineapple | corn   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, teacher
City: new-york, paris, nizza
1. the teacher is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is the journalist##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is the teacher##1
4. the teacher is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | lawyer | teacher | journalist |
| City   | paris | nizza   | new-york |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, colombian, nigerian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, may, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the australian is the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the colombian##3
4. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | australian |
| Birthday     | may     | january   | june        |

