.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, writing
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, sprite
1. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | photography | writing | baking |
| Beverage     | tea    | sprite  | lemonade   |

