.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, gardening, hiking
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, freelancer, security-guard
1. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the freelancer##1
4. the nurse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | hiking | camping   | gardening |
| Job   | freelancer   | nurse | security-guard      |

