.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, skateboard, train
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Transport     | skateboard  | train   | boat |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 